 Tuoyo Ideh, who as of late introduced artificial hair to cover his bald hair, has addressed how ladies easily wear fake hair for long periods. The Big Brother Naija star said having fake hair implies he can’t rest, he can’t wash without covering his hair with a shower cap, and to top it all off, he can’t scratch a bothersome scalp. He asked ladies how they do it, adding that ladies are trying. READ ALSO: Tuoyo Fixes Artificial Hair To Cover Baldness In his inscription, he said ladies merit everyday grants for wearing fake hair. Watch the video below.   A post shared by Tuoyo Ideh (@itstuoyoofficial) 